<h4><a href="../../../../../comments.pl_683b89ec.html" id="comment_link_2373487" name="comment_link_2373487" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(2373487)">Re:正論ではダメ</a>
<span class="score" id="comment_score_2373487">(<a href=".J-%E3%81%AB%E8%81%9E%E3%81%91-Windows-XP-%E3%81%8B%E3%82%89%E3%81%AE%E7%A7%BB%E8%A1%8C%E3%82%92%E4%BF%83%E3%81%99%E3%81%AB%E3%81%AF%E3%81%A9%E3%81%86%E3%81%99%E3%82%8C%E3%81%B0%E8%89%AF%E3%81%84" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 2373487); return false">スコア:2</a>)</span></h4>
